compute-ndays-time-in-auto:
**How we calculate this:**

**(%)** is the duration in loop mode ON or OFF divided by the total duration of basals for this time period.

**(time)** is total duration of time in loop mode ON or OFF.
compute-ndays-time-in-range:
**How we calculate this:**

**(%)** is the number of readings in range divided by all readings for this time period.

**(time)** is number of readings in range multiplied by the {{cbgLabel}} sample frequency.
compute-oneday-time-in-auto:
**How we calculate this:**

**(%)** is the duration in loop mode ON or OFF divided by the total duration of basals for this time period.

**(time)** is 24 hours multiplied by % in loop mode ON or OFF.
compute-oneday-time-in-range:
**How we calculate this:**

**(%)** is the number of readings in range divided by all readings for this time period.

**(time)** is 24 hours multiplied by % in range.
compute-total-insulin:
**How we calculate this:**

**(%)** is the respective total of basal or bolus delivery divided by total insulin delivered for this time period.
